comment: /**  * Create a NamedParameterJdbcTemplate based on the configured JdbcTemplate.  */
code: /**  * Create a NamedParameterJdbcTemplate based on the configured JdbcTemplate.  */ @Override protected void initTemplateConfig() {     JdbcTemplate jdbcTemplate = getJdbcTemplate().     if (jdbcTemplate != null) {         this.namedParameterJdbcTemplate = new NamedParameterJdbcTemplate(jdbcTemplate).     } }

comment: /**  * Return a NamedParameterJdbcTemplate wrapping the configured JdbcTemplate.  */
code: /**  * Return a NamedParameterJdbcTemplate wrapping the configured JdbcTemplate.  */ @Nullable public NamedParameterJdbcTemplate getNamedParameterJdbcTemplate() {     return this.namedParameterJdbcTemplate. }
